又係另一樣野<br />\n又好可能生命係自然而生<br />\n 可能 人係某創造者用DNA技術 砌出黎<br />\n根本有幾個層次 時序，  無所謂開始 。<br />\n呢一個宇宙時空最開始 或許連 「意識」都沒有<br />\n但天外又有天<br />\n<br />\n除左你點定義之外 仲有 無窮無盡<br />\n頭腦鐘意以佢既認知 、邏輯去 推理、分析<br />\n或者連線性發展都唔係<br />\n太多未知既可能性 根本無可能用人類今時今日既知識去推斷得出 任何正確既結果"},{"pid":"01c86dcee9a9277b60f722ddcd70371cb6a75d7f","tid":682500,"uid":8867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:03:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a4d91081bfc2e3c42bb1d32216a34d672db567d","tid":682500,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:11:08.000Z","msg":"why not both?"},{"pid":"5e08ada33c63dc1b8b44b233f990e37c05b26b02","tid":682500,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:21:06.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n俾錯負皮"},{"pid":"e38bdd5c8a2ef2d468f60ea31a5e6ae34ebbe40a","tid":682500,"uid":105166,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:05:42.000Z","msg":"個投票結果睇到啲連登仔幾撚自大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7a3c8a7155b9ebf0a300a88a2f962555a2b5c7","tid":682500,"uid":173353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"創造者未必要勁過創造物<br />\n咁亦都因為咁,我地做乜鳩走去拜個創造者?<br />\n玩Game通常都係為快樂,但有d人宜家竟然為左受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcab457cf722697aca87214736cdd55eff0af1f","tid":682500,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"竟然無熱烈討論 果係倒吊無墨水 唔會反思下既 HK g pig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0124660a85fb353a59ea051b8c7b112a432a6da2","tid":682500,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"我都想知下"},{"pid":"c28b31acc250bb1a6b6055d20ee462efd1594d91","tid":682500,"uid":334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:44:24.000Z","msg":"玩Be